    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>Keywords Fuzzy portfolio selection · Three-way decision · Cumulative prospect theory · Expected utility theory 1 Introduction as an indicator of return and the variance as an indicator of  risk.</seg>
      </tuv>
